    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/64cc9264adbd658d5f61ce6b87cbf6e8.avif?t=1747931659\" width=529 height=141 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/e33b555024b15bae9969c90ceb6778ee.poster.avif?t=1747931659\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/e33b555024b15bae9969c90ceb6778ee.webm?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/e33b555024b15bae9969c90ceb6778ee.mp4?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/19d912d8da8ac374da6dac09e66906e8.avif?t=1747931659\" width=538 height=103 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle hordes of the parasitic Vorid and evolve from a simple thief to a magic-wielding warrior. Learn spells and abilities in a fast-paced combat environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/0fc6f51dd84a963b86298444236e9a8a.poster.avif?t=1747931659\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/0fc6f51dd84a963b86298444236e9a8a.webm?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/0fc6f51dd84a963b86298444236e9a8a.mp4?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the Kingdom of Gorithia</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through expansive zones and diverse biomes where exploration is deeply encouraged and rewarded. Descend into the mysterious Forsaken Depths, embrace the enchanting forests of Myrwood, and ascend the towering peak of Mount Gorimarr in this open, interconnected world.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master Challenging Environments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash, climb and soar your way through perilous obstacles. Complete challenging platforming sections to prove your worth and gain powerful rewards. Discover secret passages and previously locked paths with your new-found abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/e3ded95806c926f49251327c96b9ebc9.avif?t=1747931659\" width=552 height=114 /></span><br>Collect and equip epic trinkets to enhance your combat prowess. Adapt and forge your unique build with 90 different equippable rings, necklaces, and shards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/749d8e9f8a8c0806d19c02f0e8be01d9.poster.avif?t=1747931659\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/749d8e9f8a8c0806d19c02f0e8be01d9.webm?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/749d8e9f8a8c0806d19c02f0e8be01d9.mp4?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Connect with Enduring Survivors</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend the resilient survivors of the fallen kingdom. Browse local wares, complete quests, and earn mighty rewards.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquer Diverse Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face over 70 different enemies and 25 powerful bosses on your quest to find your kin and restore Gorithia.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/4327f76404c144709f609ec9c15c5f37.avif?t=1747931659\" width=479 height=111 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glimpse into Gorithia's past through timegates. Meet the legendary heroes of old and defeat ancient bosses to unlock new paths, secrets, items, and lore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/f577ccb3e041233f4a3cb9bc9ff54ce5.poster.avif?t=1747931659\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/f577ccb3e041233f4a3cb9bc9ff54ce5.webm?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/f577ccb3e041233f4a3cb9bc9ff54ce5.mp4?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wield Verruna, the Living Blade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the master of Verruna, a sentient blade with a thirst for blood. Let the bound souls within the shattered sword guide you through the kingdom, helping you understand Gorithian culture, find hidden secrets, and destroy your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/342835141ee4e7f6bf29b24b63cd2904.poster.avif?t=1747931659\" width=756 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/342835141ee4e7f6bf29b24b63cd2904.webm?t=1747931659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p>",
